data.description: MUST SEE!! Beautiful remodeled property. Home is move in ready for lucky new buyers! New roof, kitchen with stainless steel appliances and laminate flooring throughout. Home is close to schools, shopping and Werner Boyce State Park. Great location and easy drive to the water, this is a home you will want to make an offer on quickly! Seller replacing brand new septic, buyer will have 6 year warranty for work.
